WEBVTT

00:00:01.680 --> 00:00:04.416
Many people face the news each morning

00:00:04.440 --> 00:00:06.896
with trepidation and dread.

00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:09.576
Every day, we read of shootings,

00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:13.496
inequality, pollution, dictatorship,

00:00:13.520 --> 00:00:16.696
war and the spread of nuclear weapons.

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:18.456
These are some of the reasons

00:00:18.480 --> 00:00:23.936
that 2016 was called
the "Worst. Year. Ever."

00:00:23.960 --> 00:00:26.536
Until 2017 claimed that record --

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:27.616
(Laughter)

00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:30.216
and left many people longing
for earlier decades,